M'Sila is mostly known for its farming. ==Divisions== The province has 15 districts and 47 communes or municipalities. ===Districts=== # Aïn El Hadjel # Aïn El Melh # Ben S'Rour # Bou Saâda # Chellal # Djebel Messaâd # Hammam Dhalaâ # Khoubana # M'Sila # Magra # Medjedel # Ouled Derradj # Ouled Sidi Brahim # Sidi Aïssa # Sidi Ameur ==References== Category:Provinces of Algeria
